# China Physical AI · Intelligence Layer

**Inside China AI · insidechinaai.substack.com · April 2026**
*By Gabrielle Chou*

---

## What this is

An interactive intelligence layer covering 66 Chinese Physical AI companies, 
scored across 15 dimensions — six layers of the technology stack, four machine 
types, and five application sectors.

Companion dataset to the visual argument:
**China Isn't Building Robots. It's Installing Operating Systems.**

---

## What the data contains

- Western Exposure Score (0–10) for each company
- Funding stage and public listing status
- Named Western customers and investors
- Export certification (CE, FDA, FCC, CAAC)
- Compliance flags — Entity List and OFAC SDN status
- One-line analytical signal per company

## How to use it

Open index.html in any browser.
Filter by sector, Western exposure level, or compliance status.
Search by company name, cluster, or named customer.
Click column headers to sort.

---

## Methodology

Western Exposure Score is a weighted composite:
- Named Western customer +4
- Western investor +3
- Export certification +1
- Foreign customer unnamed +1
- International founder degree +1

Stack Score: weighted importance across 15 dimensions covering six tech 
stack layers, four machine types, and five application sectors.

Data confidence: ●●● verified multiple independent sources · 
●● single credible source · ● estimated.

